  "prompt": "Who is the voice behind Big Boss on Big Boss reality show?",
  "response": "The voice behind **Bigg Boss** (often referred to as \"Big Boss\") is the show's narrator, who provides commentary, announces tasks, eliminations, and other key moments throughout each season. This narrator adds a dramatic and engaging layer to the show, guiding viewers through the various happenings inside the Bigg Boss house.\n\nHowever, the specific voice-over artist can vary depending on the regional version and the season of the show. Unlike the hosts (such as Salman Khan in the Hindi version), the narrator's identity is not always prominently publicized. In some cases, professional voice-over artists are employed, but their names may not be widely disclosed to the public.\n\nIf you're referring to a specific regional version or season of **Bigg Boss**, providing that information might help in identifying the narrator more accurately. Otherwise, the narrator generally remains an integral yet behind-the-scenes part of the Bigg Boss production.",
